import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { AuthContext } from '../AuthContext'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; export default function Dashboard() { const [rekening, setRekening] = useState([]); const history = useNavigate(); const { isUserAuthenticated } = React.useContext(AuthContext); if (!isUserAuthenticated) { history('/login/user'); } useEffect(() => { const fetchData = async () => { try { const response = await fetch('http://localhost:3000/rekening'); // Endpoint API Express if (!response.ok) { throw new Error('Gagal mendapatkan data rekening'); } const data = await response.json(); setRekening(data); console.log(data); } catch (error) { console.error('Error:', error); } }; fetchData(); }, []); return (
